comments: Covington (POR) establishes himself in a legal position and he is firming up when the contact with Joseph (SAC) occurs during the pick.
Covington (POR) makes marginal contact to Barnes' (SAC) arm during the drive.
Covington (POR) retreats and avoids making contact to Barnes' (SAC) arm when he swipes down during the driving shot attempt.
Kanter (POR) makes marginal contact to Barnes's (SAC) body after veering back into him on the shot attempt in the post.
Barnes (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position on Lillard (POR) during the drive.
Joseph (SAC) legally contests Lillard's (POR) jump shot attempt.
Hield (SAC) reaches in and dislodges the ball, any additional to contact to Jones's Jr. (POR) hand and body is deemed incidental.
Kanter (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during Holmes' (SAC) shot attempt near the rim.
Hield (SAC) commits a take foul on Covington (POR).
Barnes (SAC) briefly places his forearm on Covington's (POR) body as he pivots and steps away from the marginal contact.
Fox (SAC) swipes down and avoids making contact to Covington's (POR) arms.
Covington (POR) gathers the inbound pass in the frontcourt and then steps backcourt as he pivots.
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Trent Jr. (POR).
Covington (POR) commits a take foul on Fox (SAC).

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court of a free throw violation has been overturn. The ball successfully hit the bottom of the rim box and was legally in play. The whistle was blown when Kanter (POR) had the ball and therefore possession was rewarded to the Trail Blazers and the game clock was set at :03.7.
Hield (SAC) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
